  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Recipe Card</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<dl><dd></dd>\n<dd><span class=\"dablink\"><i>For complete list of Crock Pot recipes, see <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dishes\" title=\"Dishes\">Dishes</a>.</i></span></dd>\n<dd></dd>\n<dd><span class=\"dablink\"><i>For <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Warly\" title=\"Warly\">Warly</a>&#x27;s unique cooking recipes, see <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Portable_Crock_Pot\" title=\"Portable Crock Pot\">Portable Crock Pot</a>.</i></span></dd></dl>\n<p>The <b>Recipe Card</b> is an <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Item\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Item\">item</a> that allows you to learn recipes in <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i>. Can be found by naturally spawning in the world near the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Skeleton\" title=\"Skeleton\">Skeleton</a>, as well as by digging up <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Grave\" title=\"Grave\">Graves</a> or opening <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tumbleweed\" title=\"Tumbleweed\">Tumbleweeds</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sunken_Chest\" title=\"Sunken Chest\">Sunken Chest</a>. The recipe card merely lists its recipe when examined, it does not automatically add it to your <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookbook\" title=\"Cookbook\">Cookbook</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Recipe_Card#All_Recipes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">All Recipes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Recipe_Card#Tips\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Tips</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Recipe_Card#Gallery\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Gallery</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Recipe_Card#Trivia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Trivia</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"All_Recipes\">All Recipes</span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable mw-collapsible\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Icon\n</th>\n<th>Nams\n</th>\n<th>Card Recipe\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Butter_Muffin\" title=\"Butter Muffin\"><img alt=\"Butter Muffin.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Butter_Muffin.png/32px-Butter_Muffin.png?c6184a\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Butter_Muffin\" title=\"Butter Muffin\">Butter Muffin</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Butterfly_Wings\" title=\"Butterfly Wings\"><img alt=\"Butterfly Wings.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Butterfly_Wings.png/32px-Butterfly_Wings.png?b14761\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Carrot\" title=\"Carrot\"><img alt=\"Carrot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Carrot.png/32px-Carrot.png?e11b81\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Carrot\" title=\"Carrot\"><img alt=\"Carrot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Carrot.png/32px-Carrot.png?e11b81\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"